nav: | [Home](/) <% if @current_superagent && @current_superagent != @current_tenant.main_superagent -%>| <%= @current_superagent.superagent_type.titleize %>: [<%= @current_superagent.name %>](<%= @current_superagent.path %>)<% end -%><% if @current_user -%>| Logged in as [<%= @current_user.display_name %>](<%= @current_user.path %>)<% end -%> | [üîç](/search) | [<%= @unread_notification_count %>](/notifications) |

